    "causal_summary": "Make CocoIndex code-first by default. Exclude runtime spec mirrors at index time. Add `source_realpath` and `content_hash` canonical identity fields. Over-fetch `limit * 4` candidates, dedup by `(source_realpath, line_range)` or `(content_hash, line_range)`, prefer canonical paths in returned rows. Add `path_class` source-role and bounded reranking that surfaces `implementation` above `spec_research` for implementation-intent queries.",
